OL,3,CPlaid Cymru's challenge has just begun
OL,4,Cas it enters government for first time
OL,6,FAs Wales elects its first non-Labour
OL,7,Fleader, ITV News Wales Reporter Rhys
OL,8,FWilliams reacts to the historic moment
OL,9,Fand what it means for the country
OL,11,FThe chaos in Westminster was in sharp
OL,12,Fcontrast with proceedings in Cardiff
OL,13,FBay today.
OL,15,FKeir Starmer is under severe pressure,
OL,16,Fpartly due to a shattering and
OL,17,Fsymbolic defeat for Labour in Wales,
OL,18,Ffor so long its reliable heartland.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/9
