OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1778637818
OL,3,CPlaid Cymru's challenge has just begun
OL,4,Cas it enters government for first time
OL,6,FThe election of the man who broke
OL,7,FLabour's iron grip on Wales, Rhun ap
OL,8,FIorwerth, undoubtedly marks one of the
OL,9,Fmost significant moments in modern
OL,10,FWelsh political history.
OL,12,FAs well as ending a century-long
OL,13,Fwinning streak for Welsh Labour, it
OL,14,Frepresents a long-yearned-for
OL,15,Fbreakthrough for Plaid Cymru.
OL,17,FSpeaking to journalists outside Welsh
OL,18,Fgovernment headquarters after being
OL,19,Fsworn in as First Minister, Mr ap
OL,20,FIorwerth said this was a "truly
OL,21,Fmomentous" and "historic" day.
OL,26,@|D@ZOU}D@JO]}D@POU}D@YO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
