OL,3,CPlaid Cymru's challenge has just begun
OL,4,Cas it enters government for first time
OL,6,FLeaders of three of the four UK
OL,7,Fnations are now believers in leaving
OL,8,Fthe United Kingdom.
OL,10,FAsked by ITV News what message he will
OL,11,Fbe sending to the UK prime minister
OL,12,Falongside leaders in Belfast and
OL,13,FEdinburgh, the Plaid Cymru leader
OL,14,Fdidn't answer directly, but said his
OL,15,Fpriority was to the people of Wales.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
