OL,3,CPlaid Cymru's challenge has just begun
OL,4,Cas it enters government for first time
OL,6,F"My loyalty in all my time will be to
OL,7,Fthe people of Wales, yes that means
OL,8,Fworking with others where we have
OL,9,Fcommon ground across the islands but
OL,10,Fmy loyalty, always, to the citizens of
OL,11,Fthis nation."
OL,13,FMr ap Iorwerth, a former BBC political
OL,14,Fjournalist, entered the Senedd in 2013
OL,15,Fas the member for his home
OL,16,Fconstituency of Ynys Mon, off the
OL,17,Fnorth Wales coast.
