OL,3,CPlaid Cymru's challenge has just begun
OL,4,Cas it enters government for first time
OL,6,FSince taking over as leader of Plaid
OL,7,FCymru from Adam Price, his goal has
OL,8,Fbeen to reshape the party's image,
OL,9,Fpresenting it as a more credible party
OL,10,Fof government capable of appealing
OL,11,Fbeyond its traditional Welsh-speaking
OL,12,Fheartlands.
OL,14,FPlaid's media-savvy leader has long
OL,15,Fbelieved that once his party overtook
OL,16,FLabour in the polls, left-of-centre
OL,17,Fvoters would rally behind him as the
OL,18,Fbest option to block the right.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1778637818
OL,3,CPlaid Cymru's challenge has just begun
OL,4,Cas it enters government for first time
OL,6,FHis goal was to win over frustrated
OL,7,FLabour voters by focusing heavily on
OL,8,Fpublic services and the cost of living.
OL,10,FHe successfully broadened Plaid's
OL,11,Fappeal to young families with an
OL,12,Fambitious and expensive childcare
OL,13,Fpledge.
OL,15,FBut today's vote is just the beginning
OL,16,Fof the challenge.
OL,18,FPlaid Cymru has never run the Welsh
OL,19,Fgovernment before, and most of the
OL,20,Fparty's new Senedd members have never
OL,21,Fset foot in the building.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
