OL,3,CPlaid Cymru's challenge has just begun
OL,4,Cas it enters government for first time
OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FMr ap Iorwerth now faces the task of
OL,12,Fturning a party built around
OL,13,Fopposition politics into one capable
OL,14,Fof governing.
OL,16,FHe will also need to deliver his
OL,17,Fexpensive manifesto pledges, despite a
OL,18,Fworsening economic outlook.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
